quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  42,10,"Kala ko luutondir…óon e fii mun, haray √±aawoore mun nden ko ka Allah woni. Ko On moo…óon Allah, woni Joomi am; ko e Makko mi fawii, ko ka Makko kadi mi ruttorta [tuubugol]"
  42,11,"Fu…ó…óu…óo kamuuli …óin e leydi ndin. O wa…óiranii on e pittaali mon …óin genndoo…ìe, ka neemoraa…ói kadi nooneeji; Himo …óu…ó…óinira on …óum. Hay huunde yerondiraa e Makko; ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  42,12,"Ko Kanko heerori soktir…óe kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Himo wertana arsike on mo O muuyani, O …ìi…ótinana (mo O muuyani). Pellet, ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  42,13,"O sar'inanii on e diina kan, konko ko O yamirnoo Nuuhu, e kon ko Men wahayini e maa…óa, e kon ko Men yamirnoo Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa, wonnde: \"√ëi…ìnee diina kan; hara on seertaali e makka\". Kono Ko noddotaa sirkoo…ìe …ìen e mun kon, mawnii e dow ma…ì…ìe. Allah non hino su…ìanoo …óum, mo O muuyani, O fewna e Makko, kala tuuboowo"
  42,14,"∆Åe seertaano, si wanaa …ìaawo nde ganndal ngal arde e ma…ì…ìe, sabu bewre hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. Si wanaano fii Konngol ardinoongol, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e lajal ta∆¥aangal, √±aaweteno hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. Ko pellet, roninaaa…ìe Deftere nden …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe, hino e sikke fii mayre sikkitii…ìe"
  42,15,"Noddu (yim…ìe …ìen) kisan; √±ii…ìiraa no yamira…óaa non, wata a jokku mbelee…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, maakaa: \"Mi gom…óinii ko Allah jippini kon (fow) e Defte, mi yamiraama kadi, nun…óugol hakkunde mon. Allah woni Joomi amen e Joomi mon. Ko menen golle amen woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon woodani. Yeddondiral woo alaa hakkunde amen e mon. Allah moo…ìoyay e denndaandal. Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde nden"
  42,16,"∆Åen wennjiroo…ìe e diina Allah kan, …ìaawo ka ja…ìaneede, hujja ma…ì…ìe on ko meere, tikkere no fawii e ma…ì…ìe, hino woodani …ìe kadi lepte sa…ótu…óe"
  42,17,"Ko Allah woni jippiniri Deftere nden goonga, e manndakke …óen. E ko anndin maa? Hino gasa hara Darngal ngal ko ko …ìadii"
  42,18,"∆Åeya …ìe gom…óinaali ngal …ìen, hi…ìe he√±oringal; gom…óim…ìe …ìen kan, ko …ìe hulu fii maggal, e hoore hi…ìe felliti wonnde ko ngal goonga. Awa anndee won…ìe yeddondireede …ìen fii Darngal, ko pellet, …ìe wonii e nder majjere wo…ó…óunde"
  42,19,"Allah ko newanii…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Himo arsike on mo O muuyani. Ko Kanko woni Doolnu…óo, Foolu…óo On"